Privacy Policy for
Formulas
Effective Date:
January 5
th
, 2024
Thank you for using Formulas! This Privacy
Policy is designed to help you understand how we collect, use, and safeguard
your information when you use our mobile application.
1. Information We Do Not Collect:
We want to assure you that Formulas does not
collect any personal information from its users. We do not request, access, or
store any data that can be used to identify you, including but not limited to:
Names
Email addresses
Phone numbers
Location data
Device information
Usage data
2. Non-Personal Information:
While using Formulas, we may collect
non-personal information that does not directly identify you. This may include:
Aggregate usage statistics
Technical information about your device (such
as device type, operating system, etc.)
This non-personal information is collected to
help us improve the functionality and performance of the app and to better
understand how users interact with it.
3. Third-Party Services:
Formulas
does not
use third-party services, such as
analytics tools, to help us analyze how users engage with the app. These
services
do not
collect non-personal information about your use of the app,
and
they do not collect
any personally identifiable information.
4. Children's Privacy:
Formulas is not intended for use by
individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect any personal
information from children. If you believe that we may have inadvertently
collected personal information from a child, please contact us immediately, and
we will take steps to delete the information.
5. Changes to the Privacy Policy:
We reserve the right to update or modify this
Privacy Policy at any time. If we make material changes, we will notify users
through the app or via other means.
6. Contact Us:
If you have any questions or concerns about
this Privacy Policy or the privacy practices of Formulas, please contact us at
nsc@cnsapp.net
.
By using Formulas, you agree to the terms
outlined in this Privacy Policy.
Thank you for trusting Formulas with your
privacy!